&lt;li&gt;Experience with Statistical modeling such as Decision Trees, XGBoost etc. preferred&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be agile and highly collaborative, communicate impressively&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical acumen and problem solving&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
